description.p:
One aspect of this invention is a light source device. The light source device includes:
a light guide plate;
a reflector disposed under the light guide plate;
a light source unit optically coupled to the light guide plate; and
a photo luminescent film disposed between the light guide plate and the light source unit, wherein the photo luminescent film comprises at least two partitioned areas, and wherein a first fluorescent material comprised in at least one area of the at least two areas is different from a second fluorescent material comprised in the other areas.
